snippet: The top players on the free-agent market, including Zach Parise, Ryan Suter and Martin Brodeur, did not make any decisions on Sunday.
abstract: National Hockey League's free-agent signing season begins; the league's top players Zach Parise, Ryan Suter and Martin Brodeur are listening to all offers.
lead_paragraph: The top players on the free-agent market, including Zach Parise, Ryan Suter and Martin Brodeur, did not make any decisions on Sunday.

headline.seo: As Free Agency Begins, Big Moves Still Await
headline.main: As N.H.L. Free Agency Begins, Big Moves Still Await
